>\n一個人個個月洗多幾千銀<br />\n<br />\n俾又死唔俾又死<br />\n但倒番轉頭諗 咁多年你都搵唔到/培養唔到一個醒又忠誠ge 大陸仔幫你睇住<br />\n係抵你死"},{"pid":"64d91dde6bc919dd9657d79f40d51ce55404c22a","tid":795220,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪比侵侵打到傻撚左 無水想咁樣開條水喉 <br />\n笑大人個口咩"},{"pid":"47c162112312b2d6e59ec2934bded5829235f360","tid":795220,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911d1bb1bf1966efe7cdb82f881df050cd31e066","tid":795220,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd389349ed8c0d68488860176afa12e56a88f83d","tid":795220,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb835a357b9d6b4524d31fa554eeab3cb8e01e56","tid":795220,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"日日衝關果D洗唔洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"一定要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"一係咪自己計數囉 2個星期只可以開7日工 <br />\n今星期3日 下星期4日咁<br />\n<br />\n反而仲請緊人駐廠 駐大陸公司 <br />\n睇住大陸班契弟果班就頭痛<br />\n<br />\n遣散晒佢地 ? 咁邊個lead 班大陸仔？<br />\n無人睇作反都似<br />\n番3 4日 shift d 老細又好似蝕左咁<br />\n車錢 機票錢 呢樣果樣<br />\n<br />\n幫佢交大陸稅d 度縮港資台資老細又唔捨得<br />\n一個人個個月洗多幾千銀<br />\n<br />\n俾又死唔俾又死<br />\n但倒番轉頭諗 咁多年你都搵唔到/培養唔到一個醒又忠誠ge 大陸仔幫你睇住<br />\n係抵你死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"醒又忠誠ge 大陸仔＜　根本唔存在"},{"pid":"e553148e3762b649583c7de8c65364caf82bebe6","tid":795220,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47c162112312b2d6e59ec2934bded5829235f360","tid":795220,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911d1bb1bf1966efe7cdb82f881df050cd31e066","tid":795220,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd389349ed8c0d68488860176afa12e56a88f83d","tid":795220,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"一定要啦<img src=\"/assets/face